			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "BGO_Main_A\r\nClick on |Yannis| - S_WYR_OpenHand_Yannis - cb5ad2e6-40e9-4377-9669-1c4e4b1106e0 - (-45 45 -6)\r\nThis will trigger a threeway dialog between Yannis, Valerio and the player. Afterwards Valerior leaves and you can click on Yannis again to get this dialog."
